<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <title>Junior Hackathon Task - Invoice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
        }
        table {
            margin-top: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            border-spacing: 0;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        span {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .title h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .num-and-data {
            text-align: right; 
        } 
        .table-users {
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-spacing: 3px;
        }
        .table-users td {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #333333; 
            border-radius: 5px; 
        } 
        .table-invoice th {
            text-align: center;
            background: darkgrey;
        }
        .table-invoice th, .table-invoice td {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }
        .price-text {
            margin-left: 30px;
        }
        .table-tax {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .table-tax td {
            text-align: right;
        }
        .table-bank td {
            border: 1px dotted lightgray;
            padding: 3px;
        }
        .table-users-name {
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .table-users-name span {
            font-weight: normal;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .law {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .invoice-info {
            margin-top: 140px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Faktura Original</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="num-and-data">
            <p>Nomer: <span>000000{{enrolling.id}}</span></p>
            <p>Data: <span>{{ enrolling.dateAdded|date("Y-m-d") }}</span></p>   
        </div>
        <table class="table-users">
           <tr>
               <td>
                   <p>Poluchatel: {{ enrolling.student.firstName }} {{ enrolling.student.fathersName }} {{ enrolling.student.lastName }}</p>
                   <p>DDS N:</p>
                   <p>Ident. N:</p>
                   <p>Grad Varna</p>
                   <p>Adres </p> 
                   <p>MOL {{ enrolling.student.firstName }} {{ enrolling.student.fathersName }} {{ enrolling.student.lastName }} </p>
                   <p>Telefon</p>  
               </td>
               <td>
                   <p>Dostavchik: Driving Courses</p>
                   <p>DDS N:</p>
                   <p>Ident. N: 01010101</p>
                   <p>Grad Varna</p>
                   <p>Adres ul.Nikola Vapcarov</p> 
                   <p>MOL STEFAN KIRILOV STEFANOV</p>
                   <p>Telefon</p>
               </td>
           </tr>
        </table>
        <table class="table-invoice">
           <tr>
               <th style="width: 5%;">N</th>
               <th style="width: 10%;">Kod</th>
               <th style="width: 45%;">Naimenivanie na stokata / uslugata</th>
               <th style="width: 10%;">Mqrka</th>
               <th style="width: 10%;">Kolich.</th>
               <th style="width: 10%;">Cena</th>
               <th style="width: 10%;">Suma</th>
           </tr>
           <tr>
               <td style="width: 5%; text-align: center;">1</td>
               <td style="width: 10%;"></td>
               <td style="width: 45%;">{{ enrolling.course.title}}</td>
               <td style="width: 10%; text-align: center;">br.</td>
               <td style="width: 10%; text-align: right;">1.00</td>
               <td style="width: 10%; text-align: right;">{{ enrolling.course.price }}</td>
               <td style="width: 10%; text-align: right;">{{ enrolling.course.price }}</td>
           </tr>
        </table>   
        <table class="table-tax">
            <tr>
                <td style="width: 55%;">
                </td>
                <td style="width: 30%;">
                    <p>Danichna osnova:</p>
                    <p>DDS 0%:</p>
                    <p>Suma za plashtane:</p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 15%;">
                    <p>{{ enrolling.course.price}}</p>
                    <p>0.00</p>
                    <p>{{ enrolling.course.price}}</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="price-text">
            <p><span>Slovom:</span> {{ enrolling.course.priceText}}</p>
        </div>
        <table class="table-bank">
           <tr>
               <td style="width: 60%;">
                   <p>Data na danichnoto sibitie: {{ enrolling.dateAdded|date("Y-m-d") }}</p>
                   <p>Osnovanie za nenachisl. na DDS:</p>
                   <p>Opisanie na sdelkata:</p>
                   <p>Mqsto na sdelkata: Varna</p>  
               </td>
               <td style="width: 40%;">
                   <p>Plashtane: V broi</p>
                   <p>IBAN:</p> 
                   <p>Banka:</p>
                   <p>Bankov cod:</p>
               </td>
           </tr>
        </table>
        <table class="table-users-name">
            <tr>
                <td style="width: 55% padding: 5px;">
                    <p>Poluchil: {{ enrolling.student.firstName }} {{ enrolling.student.fathersName }} {{ enrolling.student.lastName }}</p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 45%;">
                    <p>Sistavil: <span>{{ app.user.firstName }} {{ app.user.fathersName }} {{ app.user.lastName }}</span></p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="law">
            <p>Siglasno 4l. 6, al. 1 ot Zakona za S4etovodstvoto, 4l. 114 ot ZDDS i 4l. 78 ot PPZDDS pechatit i podpisit ne sa zadiljitelni rekviziti viv fakturata.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="invoice-info">
            <hr />
            <p>Driving Courses, telefon: 123456987, http://www.courses.com</p>
        </div> 
    </div>

</body>
</html>
